Title: Fortress Mk II (Titanium 24600)
Description:
A fortress with a lot of mark II armored bots, a spidertron 5000, flameraptors and other enemies.

Features:
1. Main area - mainly mark II hammers
2. Side yards - a mark 3 armored hammer and a jet armored archer in each yard
2. Roof - a lot of archers, can be accessed from the jump pad in the back
3. Bottom area - flameraptor flame archers and a kickbot, can be accessed from the back

Have fun!
